fabric.messages

Class MessageToStoreHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • fabric.messages.AbstractMessageServer
      • fabric.messages.MessageToStoreHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageHandler, java.lang.Runnable

    public abstract class MessageToStoreHandler
extends AbstractMessageServer
    This abstract class acts as a visitor for MessagesToStore. It also documents the list of all messages that a store needs to be able to handle. The methods all have the form:
     public Response handle(Principal, Message)
   throws FabricException
    and there is one such method for each message type that the store handles.
